Alexandre Rousseau

  • son of André (Gide) and Jean-Jacques Rousseau (OC)
    • second oldest of his family
  • boy, cis for now
    • he/him
  • bisexual
  • starts the series at 12 and ends at 19
  • born July 24th, 2003
  • Namesake: Alexandre Dumas
  • Ability: Count of Monte Cristo
  • Affiliation: Eventually affiliates with the Apprentices of the ADA and later on the ADA itself, as well as the Gunslinger Kids
  • Level at which I think about him: low
  • Brief Notes: He's Ladybird Rousseau's immediate younger brother (as in, she's the oldest of the family, and he's right behind her in age), so he was the most affected of the children when she disappeared right at the end of 2015. They were also very close as siblings, further complicating things. He, like the rest of his family, has no idea where she is or what could have happened to her, only that the last time he saw her, she was hanging around a strange man who gave Alexandre bad vibes.
